U.K. Stocks Decline in London ; FTSE 100 Drops 0.4 Percent

-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 
2011-09-08T12:38:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/u-k-stocks-decline-in-london-ftse-100-drops-0-4-percent.html
U.K. stocks retreated, sending the
FTSE 100 Index down 0.5 percent to 5,292.09 at 1:37 p.m. in
 London . The gauge has swung between gains and losses at least
five times today and earlier rallied as much as 1 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
